Machine learning allows computers to learn and make decision without being explicitly programmed.
Feeding data into algorithms to identify patterns and make predictions on new data. 
The various applications are 1)image recognition 2)speech processing 3) language translation ,etc .
The questions is why do we need machine learning :-
The answer to this question is that traditional programming requires exact instructions and doesn't handle complex task like understanding images or language well.
It can't efficiently process large amounts of data. Machine Learning solves these problems by learning from examples and making predictions without fixed rules.
1)Solving Complex Business problems 
Traditional programming struggles with task life language understanding and medical diagnosis.ML learns from data and predicts outcomes easily.
